com.dynatrace.apm.uem.mobile.android
Class JsNativeBridge

java.lang.Object
  com.dynatrace.apm.uem.mobile.android.JsNativeBridge

public class JsNativeBridge
extends java.lang.Object

This class is the ADK's JavaScript-Native bridge enabling the use of the ADK from javascript. Most of the methods defined in this class mirror those found in UemAction and DynatraceUEM classes. Some noticeable differences include:

  • enterAction returns an action ID rather than the action itself
  • Method in context of an UemAction requires the action ID
  • Instead of overload reportValue(...), there are specific methods to report different data types
When adding a new JS interface method here, be sure to add the same one to JsNativeBridgeAPI17.

setRequestCookieForAction

public int setRequestCookieForAction(java.lang.String actionId)
Indicate to dT web server agent to begin grouping web requests until the given action is closed

Parameters:
actionId - The ID of the action wrapping web requests executed while it is open. If null, an attempt is made to determine the most recent action and use it if there is one.
Returns:
DynatraceUEM.CPWR_UemOn if successful. Otherwise, DynatraceUEM.CPWR_Error_ActionNotFound or one of the return codes from DynatraceUEM.uemCaptureStatus()
